node.text:
These kibbles are the best... Fudge usually do not kibbles without an egg or some cheese. But, with this one, she could just eat it ALL ! They love it! Its Turkey & Sweet potato flavour. Where can we get this in Singapore? Or do we need to order overseas?
.
.
.
@thewoofagency @pawjourr @petsclubsg #thewoofagency #sponsored #bronco
So happy that Fudge loves it!! Perromart sells this brand in Turkey and Sweet potato!! Enjoy!❤️
